\fs36 \ul \ulc3 Scope: 
\fs26 \ulnone \
\
This alpha has expanded the functionality of Last Stand Cloud in a major way. Now Last Stand Cloud is starting to take shape into its professional form and now the work done for this version will carry it to the future. Remote, peer to peer routing and being able to connect to multiple cloud from one client are not an immediate objective, but they are going to go into development soon after alpha version 3. This update was largely based on the user interface and refinement of access and security. Any faults in the user interface or bugs/vulnerabilities in the security are what we are going to look for. \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\qc\partightenfactor0

